1
00:01:23,059 --> 00:01:30,515
[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]

2
00:01:31,991 --> 00:01:36,243
[Episode 26]

3
00:01:36,243 --> 00:01:37,243
I am just an innocent woman,

4
00:01:37,243 --> 00:01:38,263
lack of knowledge.

5
00:01:38,263 --> 00:01:39,603
Advisor, please forgive me.

6
00:01:41,443 --> 00:01:43,263
Since it is not the Chief Administrator
who wants the man,

7
00:01:43,263 --> 00:01:44,523
then it's easier to handle.

8
00:01:45,283 --> 00:01:47,563
Anyway, Master. Mi is
seriously injured like this,

9
00:01:47,563 --> 00:01:48,823
can't go anywhere.

10
00:01:48,823 --> 00:01:50,703
Advisor, please wait

11
00:01:50,703 --> 00:01:52,223
until his injuries are slightly better,

12
00:01:52,223 --> 00:01:54,223
then take the official paper to bring him,

13
00:01:54,223 --> 00:01:56,283
to prevent people to think

14
00:01:56,283 --> 00:01:57,923
that someone is slaughtering the merchants

15
00:01:57,923 --> 00:02:00,803
in order to steal the money and goods.

16
00:02:03,563 --> 00:02:05,603
Madam, you are indeed kind.

17
00:02:07,963 --> 00:02:10,323
Just make sure not to get yourself involved.

18
00:02:11,963 --> 00:02:13,003
You are funny.

19
00:02:13,683 --> 00:02:15,003
It is said that good and
evil have their own rewards.

20
00:02:15,603 --> 00:02:17,423
I have never slaughtered in the city
or trafficked in goods unlawfully.

21
00:02:17,423 --> 00:02:18,923
How could I get myself involved?

22
00:02:20,123 --> 00:02:21,823
There are gods watching.

23
00:02:21,823 --> 00:02:23,243
Only those

24
00:02:23,243 --> 00:02:25,563
who are full of sin and greatly evil

25
00:02:25,563 --> 00:02:26,803
will have their evil actions repaid with evil.

26
00:02:27,603 --> 00:02:29,803
The souls of those who died at their hands

27
00:02:29,803 --> 00:02:31,583
are waiting for these bastards
in the underworld

28
00:02:31,583 --> 00:02:35,183
to tear out their hearts and torture them.

29
00:02:35,183 --> 00:02:37,563
Don't worry for me.

30
00:02:46,043 --> 00:02:47,723
Madam, I will remember

31
00:02:48,523 --> 00:02:51,123
what you said today.

32
00:02:57,843 --> 00:02:59,323
Master. Mi.

33
00:03:03,563 --> 00:03:05,760
Master. Mi can't stand this fierce medicine.

34
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,823
Save him.

35
00:03:06,823 --> 00:03:08,803
We can't let him die for no reason.

36
00:03:39,603 --> 00:03:41,843
Physician Han, keep treating him.

37
00:03:42,483 --> 00:03:43,783
If he were to die now,

38
00:03:43,783 --> 00:03:45,363
many things are not clear,

39
00:03:45,363 --> 00:03:46,503
what should we do then?

40
00:03:46,503 --> 00:03:47,552
Save him now.

41
00:04:10,603 --> 00:04:11,843
Madam.

42
00:04:11,843 --> 00:04:12,928
Please forgive me

43
00:04:13,923 --> 00:04:15,603
for not being able to
bring the dead back to life.

44
00:04:21,003 --> 00:04:22,203
Don't be sad, Madam.

45
00:04:23,403 --> 00:04:24,763
Everyone has their own destiny,

46
00:04:25,443 --> 00:04:27,763
that's what some lowly people deserve.

47
00:04:28,603 --> 00:04:32,083
It's not something that can be
changed by anyone's words.

48
00:04:34,603 --> 00:04:35,643
It's still too early

49
00:04:36,443 --> 00:04:38,723
to talk about destiny.

50
00:04:40,883 --> 00:04:42,683
Madam, I guess you still
have matters to take care of.

51
00:04:44,043 --> 00:04:46,443
Then I won't bother you any longer.

52
00:05:02,683 --> 00:05:03,776
What is it?

53
00:05:11,723 --> 00:05:13,683
Wang Wendu is filled with greed,

54
00:05:13,683 --> 00:05:16,483
slaughtering the merchants
in the city for money.

55
00:05:17,123 --> 00:05:19,123
However, Su Dingfang and Pei Xingjian

56
00:05:19,123 --> 00:05:20,723
are not willing to join in.

57
00:05:22,003 --> 00:05:23,763
In order to force Su Dingfang accepts,

58
00:05:24,283 --> 00:05:27,283
Wang Wendu frames Master. Mi as a Dadu spy,

59
00:05:27,883 --> 00:05:29,103
also detains Pei Xingjian

60
00:05:29,103 --> 00:05:30,403
in the name of

61
00:05:30,403 --> 00:05:31,623
ineffective dispatch of provisions

62
00:05:31,623 --> 00:05:33,203
and tries to convict him.

63
00:05:34,003 --> 00:05:36,423
Later he escorts Pei Xingjian to Xizhou,

64
00:05:36,423 --> 00:05:38,303
wanting to use the knife of Qu family

65
00:05:38,303 --> 00:05:40,203
to remove Pei Xingjian.

66
00:05:57,344 --> 00:05:58,363
Mr. Bai San.

67
00:05:58,363 --> 00:05:59,456
Shopkeeper.

68
00:05:59,456 --> 00:06:00,543
Is the battle over?

69
00:06:00,543 --> 00:06:02,063
Is Senior Official Pei safe and sound?

70
00:06:02,063 --> 00:06:03,463
The Tang army has already returned.

71
00:06:03,463 --> 00:06:05,823
The Chancellor is detained in the army.

72
00:06:05,823 --> 00:06:08,923
The Chancellor has gone through great pains
to get provisions and hasn't received merits,

73
00:06:08,923 --> 00:06:09,963
how did he end up getting detained?

74
00:06:09,963 --> 00:06:12,083
Yes, what should we do?

75
00:06:13,883 --> 00:06:14,976
In the past three months,

76
00:06:15,683 --> 00:06:17,323
Shouyue has worked pretty hard,

77
00:06:17,323 --> 00:06:20,203
using just the few tens of thousands
of laborers and carriages that he had at hand,

78
00:06:20,203 --> 00:06:22,443
to support the provisions for
the army of a hundred thousand,

79
00:06:22,443 --> 00:06:23,583
but in the end,

80
00:06:23,583 --> 00:06:26,163
what he got in return is a bloody massacre

81
00:06:26,163 --> 00:06:28,163
and an accusation
of ineffective dispatch of the provisions.

82
00:06:28,923 --> 00:06:30,343
Madam, don't worry.

83
00:06:30,343 --> 00:06:32,523
Although Deputy Commander Wang Wendu
is up to something evil,

84
00:06:32,523 --> 00:06:33,963
the Chancellor has a reputation,

85
00:06:33,963 --> 00:06:35,923
has even won the trust
of people in the military.

86
00:06:36,483 --> 00:06:38,403
The soldiers are extremely caring
towards the Chancellor.

87
00:06:38,403 --> 00:06:39,424
Therefore,

88
00:06:40,203 --> 00:06:41,323
he has not suffered too much.

89
00:06:44,923 --> 00:06:47,403
Calculating the days, the queen
must have already received the news.

90
00:06:47,403 --> 00:06:49,883
Perhaps His Majesty's decree has been issue.

91
00:06:49,883 --> 00:06:51,903
We just need to wait a few more days,

92
00:06:51,903 --> 00:06:53,243
there will be good news.

93
00:06:54,563 --> 00:06:55,583
The matters this time,

94
00:06:55,583 --> 00:06:56,723
I must thank you.

95
00:06:57,323 --> 00:06:59,163
Your trip this time was indeed dangerous.

96
00:06:59,683 --> 00:07:01,483
Thanks to the Chancellor,

97
00:07:01,483 --> 00:07:03,323
those of us who prepare provisions for army

98
00:07:03,323 --> 00:07:04,723
could escape unscathed.

99
00:07:05,283 --> 00:07:06,336
What do you mean?

100
00:07:06,963 --> 00:07:08,983
The army provisions officer sent by Wang Wendu

101
00:07:08,983 --> 00:07:11,123
intended to detain all those merchants.

102
00:07:12,003 --> 00:07:13,463
Fortunately, the Chancellor said,

103
00:07:13,463 --> 00:07:14,523
" Deputy Director Wang

104
00:07:14,523 --> 00:07:16,843
if you want to have no more provisions
on the return journey,

105
00:07:16,843 --> 00:07:18,083
then detain people as you wish."

106
00:07:18,603 --> 00:07:20,563
After pondering for a long time,
that officer still did not dare to do so,

107
00:07:20,563 --> 00:07:22,243
so only the Chancellor alone is detained.

108
00:07:23,643 --> 00:07:25,123
They intended to interrogate
the Chancellor day and night

109
00:07:25,123 --> 00:07:26,303
to convict his crime.

110
00:07:26,303 --> 00:07:28,803
But once the word about the ineffective
dispatch of provisions spread,

111
00:07:28,803 --> 00:07:31,383
Li Lang, who's in charge of
the military granary, immediately fell out.

112
00:07:31,383 --> 00:07:33,523
Because the Chancellor does not
hold any position in the military granary,

113
00:07:33,523 --> 00:07:35,323
just helping Mr. Li with what he's doing.

114
00:07:35,323 --> 00:07:37,823
If he was guilty
of ineffective dispatch of provisions,

115
00:07:37,823 --> 00:07:39,323
how could Mr. Li be innocent?

116
00:07:40,723 --> 00:07:41,923
The soldiers in the military granary
couldn't stand by and seeing it,

117
00:07:41,923 --> 00:07:42,983
seizing the chance to make a noise.

118
00:07:42,983 --> 00:07:45,643
Wang Wendu's soldiers didn't
dare to commit the public anger,

119
00:07:45,643 --> 00:07:48,523
plus, Mr. An had managed things
thoroughly, from top to bottom,

120
00:07:48,523 --> 00:07:50,083
thus the matter was postponed.

121
00:07:52,963 --> 00:07:54,483
Wang Wendu is filled with greed.

122
00:07:54,483 --> 00:07:55,923
First, in order to make money,

123
00:07:55,923 --> 00:07:57,603
he slaughtered the merchants in the city.

124
00:07:58,283 --> 00:08:00,863
Then he framed Master. Mi as a Dadu spy.

125
00:08:00,863 --> 00:08:02,463
Now, he has arrested Shouyue

126
00:08:02,463 --> 00:08:05,003
to force General Su Dingfang to submit.

127
00:08:05,003 --> 00:08:06,503
He even took the initiative

128
00:08:06,503 --> 00:08:07,683
to frame him for a crime.

129
00:08:08,723 --> 00:08:10,123
Is Protector-General Qu aware of this?

130
00:08:13,803 --> 00:08:15,963
Someone in the army tipped me off,

131
00:08:15,963 --> 00:08:18,363
saying Deputy Director Wang will
send the Chancellor back to Xizhou.

132
00:08:19,643 --> 00:08:22,443
Probably he wanted to use
Qu family's knife to kill people.

133
00:08:23,403 --> 00:08:25,523
That's why the two of us rushed back,

134
00:08:25,523 --> 00:08:26,923
so you can be mentally prepared.

135
00:08:30,123 --> 00:08:32,003
Both Protector-General Qu and Minister
are not fools.

136
00:08:32,003 --> 00:08:33,803
How could they be used by others?

137
00:08:34,483 --> 00:08:36,043
It's just the Chancellor is being
remanded back to Xizhou,

138
00:08:36,563 --> 00:08:37,683
saying Protector-General Qu

139
00:08:37,683 --> 00:08:39,203
is afraid of offending those generals.

140
00:08:40,043 --> 00:08:41,583
Even if the decree arrives soon,

141
00:08:41,583 --> 00:08:43,523
what should we do these days?

142
00:08:44,283 --> 00:08:46,843
Protector-General Qu's original intention must be
to avoid making things difficult for Shouyue.

143
00:08:46,843 --> 00:08:48,883
All we need to do is to find him a reason.

144
00:08:56,283 --> 00:08:57,312
I'll take care of it

145
00:08:58,003 --> 00:08:59,283
from here.

146
00:09:01,243 --> 00:09:04,003
Trust me and I'm not going to let
anything happen to Shouyue.

147
00:09:05,803 --> 00:09:07,623
You and Mr. Bai San have had a hard journey,

148
00:09:07,623 --> 00:09:09,123
please go back and rest for now.

149
00:09:10,203 --> 00:09:11,763
Please send my sister
and Mr. Bai San off for me.

150
00:09:11,763 --> 00:09:12,800
Yes.

151
00:09:34,176 --> 00:09:38,944
[Pei's Mansion]

152
00:09:39,603 --> 00:09:40,704
Mr. Bai San.

153
00:09:46,923 --> 00:09:48,003
Is Cheng doing well?

154
00:09:48,643 --> 00:09:49,728
Cheng?

155
00:09:57,803 --> 00:10:00,443
Cheng is staying with the Chancellor,
he's fine.

156
00:10:03,523 --> 00:10:04,576
Thank you.

157
00:10:46,208 --> 00:10:47,232
My lady.

158
00:11:21,203 --> 00:11:22,283
As the wise men once said,

159
00:11:22,843 --> 00:11:24,123
in order for a tree to grow,

160
00:11:24,843 --> 00:11:26,083
its roots must be well-anchored;

161
00:11:26,803 --> 00:11:28,083
for a river to flow far,

162
00:11:28,603 --> 00:11:29,923
its headwaters must be properly dredged;

163
00:11:30,723 --> 00:11:32,243
to hope the nation is content,

164
00:11:32,243 --> 00:11:33,723
righteousness must be practiced;

165
00:11:34,563 --> 00:11:36,843
a nation can be content
without prevalent righteousness,

166
00:11:36,843 --> 00:11:37,963
how is that possible?

167
00:11:38,816 --> 00:11:39,840
Therefore,

168
00:11:40,363 --> 00:11:42,243
in order to restrain those
who obtain high merits,

169
00:11:42,243 --> 00:11:44,243
the former emperor developed
the system of punishment.

170
00:11:45,883 --> 00:11:48,443
Currently, the Commander
of the Congshan Route, Cheng Zhijie,

171
00:11:49,163 --> 00:11:50,603
and Deputy Director Wang Wendu,

172
00:11:51,883 --> 00:11:53,043
have been promoted

173
00:11:54,083 --> 00:11:55,583
and entrusted with the duty of a general.

174
00:11:55,583 --> 00:11:57,263
But they fail to abide
by the law with integrity

175
00:11:57,263 --> 00:11:58,843
to repay His Majesty's grace.

176
00:11:58,843 --> 00:12:00,423
They are greedy, brutal, and indulgent.

177
00:12:00,423 --> 00:12:02,123
Because of their own selfish desires,

178
00:12:02,123 --> 00:12:03,883
they slaughtered within
the walled cities of the Tang dynasty,

179
00:12:04,563 --> 00:12:05,903
killed thousands of people,

180
00:12:05,903 --> 00:12:07,203
and plundered goods without measure,

181
00:12:07,203 --> 00:12:08,443
letting people outside the territory

182
00:12:08,963 --> 00:12:10,283
bear the hatred of a thousand years,

183
00:12:11,043 --> 00:12:12,443
and the honest officials

184
00:12:12,443 --> 00:12:13,803
suffer from an unjust accusation.

185
00:12:14,403 --> 00:12:15,943
They wish to deceive His Majesty,

186
00:12:15,943 --> 00:12:17,923
they are especially condemnable.

187
00:12:18,723 --> 00:12:19,776
My lady.

188
00:12:22,203 --> 00:12:23,243
I beg Your Majesty,

189
00:12:24,043 --> 00:12:25,523
with the great power,

190
00:12:25,523 --> 00:12:27,083
to punish the criminal according to the law,

191
00:12:27,963 --> 00:12:29,203
letting people of the Western Regions

192
00:12:30,163 --> 00:12:31,563
to feel the grace of Your Majesty.

193
00:12:44,352 --> 00:12:45,408
What's wrong?

194
00:12:46,923 --> 00:12:49,243
My lady, you should take a look outside.

195
00:13:08,083 --> 00:13:09,203
Madam, nice to meet you.

196
00:13:10,123 --> 00:13:12,463
Hearing that the Chancellor is detained,

197
00:13:12,463 --> 00:13:13,683
the people of Xizhou are really indignant,

198
00:13:14,283 --> 00:13:17,443
wanting to go the Protector-General's Mansion
to petition for the Chancellor.

199
00:13:18,163 --> 00:13:19,643
I think this matter is important,

200
00:13:20,483 --> 00:13:22,163
so I want to ask your advice.

201
00:13:22,163 --> 00:13:24,363
- Right. Please give us advice.
- Right.

202
00:13:25,683 --> 00:13:27,083
On behalf of Shouyue, I thank

203
00:13:27,083 --> 00:13:29,203
all your deep affection.

204
00:13:29,963 --> 00:13:31,003
You arrived just in time.

205
00:13:31,763 --> 00:13:33,283
I have a favor to ask.

206
00:13:52,403 --> 00:13:54,683
This is a petition written by me,

207
00:13:55,443 --> 00:13:58,223
if you can sign this petition,

208
00:13:58,223 --> 00:13:59,663
you could help Shouyue.

209
00:13:59,663 --> 00:14:00,672
No problem.

210
00:14:00,672 --> 00:14:02,783
Yes, every household,

211
00:14:02,783 --> 00:14:04,023
regardless of men, women, old or young,

212
00:14:04,023 --> 00:14:06,483
everyone in Xizhou would sign their names.

213
00:14:06,483 --> 00:14:07,823
Right, we'd sign it.

214
00:14:07,823 --> 00:14:10,003
We'd sign it.

215
00:14:10,003 --> 00:14:12,523
We'd sign it.

216
00:14:35,723 --> 00:14:38,503
We'd sign it.

217
00:14:38,503 --> 00:14:39,584
Everyone.

218
00:14:41,923 --> 00:14:43,003
This petition

219
00:14:43,723 --> 00:14:45,523
will eventually be presented to

220
00:14:45,523 --> 00:14:46,923
His Majesty in Chang'an.

221
00:14:47,843 --> 00:14:49,623
If you sign your names

222
00:14:49,623 --> 00:14:50,963
on this petition,

223
00:14:51,563 --> 00:14:53,723
will offend those who frame the Chancellor.

224
00:14:58,643 --> 00:15:00,523
If you could jointly sign it,

225
00:15:00,523 --> 00:15:01,963
I would be grateful.

226
00:15:02,643 --> 00:15:05,843
If you are concerned about
the safety of yourself or your family,

227
00:15:06,363 --> 00:15:09,123
I won't mind it either.

228
00:15:26,523 --> 00:15:28,160
Ni, bring the brush pen and ink.

229
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,184
Yes.

230
00:15:29,184 --> 00:15:30,336
No need to bring the brush pen and ink.

231
00:16:45,923 --> 00:16:47,803
With the foundation of the people petition,

232
00:16:47,803 --> 00:16:49,903
Protector-General Qu took this as a reason

233
00:16:49,903 --> 00:16:52,963
to release Pei Xingjian home on the second day.

234
00:17:06,963 --> 00:17:08,123
What happened?

235
00:17:08,963 --> 00:17:10,243
How did I hear that the people of Xizhou today

236
00:17:10,243 --> 00:17:12,363
embraced Pei Xingjian
all the way back to Pei's Mansion,

237
00:17:13,363 --> 00:17:14,603
even singing and dancing on the way?

238
00:17:15,603 --> 00:17:16,963
This is outrageous.

239
00:17:18,083 --> 00:17:20,083
Why didn't you care about it?

240
00:17:22,003 --> 00:17:24,263
Didn't Deputy Director Wang notify in advance?

241
00:17:24,263 --> 00:17:26,003
As soon as Pei Xingjian entered Xizhou,

242
00:17:26,003 --> 00:17:27,603
he has to be immediately jailed
and severely interrogated.

243
00:17:28,163 --> 00:17:29,723
Be jailed and severely interrogated?

244
00:17:30,944 --> 00:17:32,083
No way.

245
00:17:32,083 --> 00:17:33,443
What do you mean?

246
00:17:36,163 --> 00:17:37,883
Did Kudi Liuli say something

247
00:17:38,603 --> 00:17:39,843
to Protector-General today,

248
00:17:41,203 --> 00:17:42,683
and you changed your mind?

249
00:17:43,883 --> 00:17:47,243
Now Pei Xingjian is someone
that we cannot touch or interrogate.

250
00:17:48,043 --> 00:17:49,383
Not only me,

251
00:17:49,383 --> 00:17:50,643
but also my father.

252
00:17:53,883 --> 00:17:55,523
If you must know why,

253
00:17:56,203 --> 00:17:57,283
let me show you.

254
00:17:59,083 --> 00:18:00,160
Okay.

255
00:18:10,083 --> 00:18:11,363
Minister.

256
00:18:36,563 --> 00:18:38,003
Mr. Su, you arrived just in time.

257
00:18:38,643 --> 00:18:41,043
Even though I have written a letter
to Deputy Director Wang,

258
00:18:41,043 --> 00:18:43,163
you need to see it

259
00:18:43,163 --> 00:18:45,203
for yourself.

260
00:18:45,723 --> 00:18:46,923
When you get to the camp,

261
00:18:47,443 --> 00:18:49,923
you can tell the Chief Administrator in detail.

262
00:18:50,643 --> 00:18:51,648
This is…

263
00:18:52,363 --> 00:18:53,443
This is

264
00:18:53,963 --> 00:18:55,123
the people petition,

265
00:18:55,123 --> 00:18:56,863
which is written

266
00:18:56,863 --> 00:18:58,563
with the blood of the people.

267
00:18:58,563 --> 00:18:59,903
This morning,

268
00:18:59,903 --> 00:19:01,883
