if we are to imprison Pei Xingjian,

271
00:19:06,003 --> 00:19:07,323
she would lead

272
00:19:07,323 --> 00:19:09,123
the merchants and monks of Xizhou

273
00:19:09,123 --> 00:19:11,123
holding up this people petition all the way

274
00:19:11,683 --> 00:19:13,083
to Chang'an.

275
00:19:13,763 --> 00:19:15,243
She…

276
00:19:15,243 --> 00:19:17,083
How dare she act so recklessly!

277
00:19:18,483 --> 00:19:20,143
