report this to Deputy Director Wang.

284
00:19:35,783 --> 00:19:38,443
If Deputy Director Wang
wants to take her to jail,

285
00:19:39,083 --> 00:19:42,123
then let him send someone to do so.

286
00:19:42,123 --> 00:19:44,843
I will not stop you.

287
00:19:45,883 --> 00:19:46,883
