292
00:19:59,803 --> 00:20:01,283
If you take her to jail now,

293
00:20:01,923 --> 00:20:03,883
you can't hide it to…

294
00:20:18,003 --> 00:20:19,103
What?

295
00:20:19,103 --> 00:20:20,443
You have been away from
Chang'an for a long time,

296
00:20:20,443 --> 00:20:22,723
