297
00:20:22,723 --> 00:20:24,283
This Ms. Kudi is very powerful,

298
00:20:25,203 --> 00:20:27,643
she has a deep friendship with the queen.

299
00:20:27,643 --> 00:20:29,483
Even the Princess Linhai

300
00:20:29,483 --> 00:20:30,883
could do nothing about her.

301
00:20:31,723 --> 00:20:33,603
