you can turn Xizhou into Dadu overnight.

305
00:20:47,123 --> 00:20:48,243
Otherwise,

306
00:20:48,243 --> 00:20:50,783
if anyone dares to touch a hair of hers,

307
00:20:50,783 --> 00:20:53,483
everyone in Chang'an will
know about it at once.

308
00:20:54,203 --> 00:20:55,363
In this way,

309
00:20:56,523 --> 00:20:58,483
are you going to sit idly by

310
00:20:59,043 --> 00:21:00,963
letting them get away with it?

311
00:21:02,083 --> 00:21:03,563
Mr. Su, do not blame me.

312
00:21:03,563 --> 00:21:06,583
I have always been timid.

313
00:21:06,583 --> 00:21:07,923
In the past half month,

314
00:21:07,923 --> 00:21:09,743
I think we have
a pretty tight lockdown in Xizhou.

315
00:21:09,743 --> 00:21:11,083
But there are always

316
00:21:11,083 --> 00:21:13,923
some merchants and monks going east.

317
00:21:13,923 --> 00:21:15,763
Who knows if they

318
00:21:15,763 --> 00:21:18,403
would take such a people petition?

319
00:21:19,963 --> 00:21:21,963
If anyone left the city half a month ago

320
00:21:21,963 --> 00:21:23,643
and traveled day and night,

321
00:21:23,643 --> 00:21:24,923
I'm afraid at this moment,

322
00:21:25,443 --> 00:21:27,003
they are already not far from Chang'an.

323
00:21:36,352 --> 00:21:37,376
I…

324
00:21:38,883 --> 00:21:40,483
I'll go and tell the Chief Administrator.

325
00:21:54,683 --> 00:21:55,744
Chongyu.

326
00:21:56,803 --> 00:21:57,963
In your opinion,

327
00:21:59,043 --> 00:22:01,723
could this Ms. Kudi really

328
00:22:02,403 --> 00:22:05,003
send someone to take
another copy of the people petition?

329
00:22:05,883 --> 00:22:08,003
I do not know whether
there is another blood letter.

