333
00:22:35,323 --> 00:22:36,416
Come often when you're free.

334
00:22:40,243 --> 00:22:41,312
Come often when you're free.

335
00:22:52,448 --> 00:22:53,523
My lady, rest assured.

336
00:22:53,523 --> 00:22:55,603
My lady, go inside and accompany your husband.

337
00:22:55,603 --> 00:22:57,123
We're here.

338
00:22:57,963 --> 00:22:59,883
Cheng, you've also worked hard.
Go and take some rest.

339
00:23:01,083 --> 00:23:02,400
You give this to me and hurry up to rest.

340
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:03,603
It's okay.

341
00:23:03,603 --> 00:23:05,723
I spent so much time in the camp with Master,

342
00:23:05,723 --> 00:23:07,123
it's so difficult for me
to come back to see you…

343
00:23:10,083 --> 00:23:11,763
all.

344
00:23:11,763 --> 00:23:13,803
I'm not tired and I'm happy.

345
00:23:18,003 --> 00:23:19,043
I'll leave it to you.

346
00:23:19,563 --> 00:23:20,704
Yes.

347
00:23:25,643 --> 00:23:26,883
Sister.

348
00:23:26,883 --> 00:23:28,123
Dance with me once more.

349
00:23:28,763 --> 00:23:29,903
Lady Yun.

350
00:23:29,903 --> 00:23:31,923
