between My lady and My Master.

351
00:23:31,923 --> 00:23:33,563
You better find someone else to dance with.

352
00:23:36,723 --> 00:23:37,728
Sister.

353
00:23:42,112 --> 00:23:43,203
Tan.

354
00:23:43,203 --> 00:23:45,603
Don't you want to learn to dance?
I'll teach you.

355
00:23:45,603 --> 00:23:46,883
