365
00:24:10,368 --> 00:24:11,392
Sanniang.

366
00:24:11,963 --> 00:24:13,163
What are you all doing?

367
00:24:13,163 --> 00:24:14,163
Dance.

368
00:24:23,403 --> 00:24:25,443
Today, my brother-in-law came back.

369
00:24:26,763 --> 00:24:27,803
