in over a hundred days and nights.

376
00:25:12,563 --> 00:25:13,963
I'm going to make it up today.

377
00:25:18,912 --> 00:25:19,968
As long as you want to,

378
00:25:20,923 --> 00:25:22,443
I will answer you a thousand times.

379
00:25:33,203 --> 00:25:34,208
Liuli.

380
00:25:36,243 --> 00:25:37,483
I know you're worried about me,

381
00:25:38,592 --> 00:25:39,616
but

382
00:25:40,123 --> 00:25:41,443
