383
00:25:42,723 --> 00:25:44,063
It's just a small cut.

384
00:25:44,063 --> 00:25:45,123
It doesn't hurt much.

385
00:25:47,360 --> 00:25:48,403
You're

386
00:25:49,723 --> 00:25:51,603
putting yourself in danger by doing this.

387
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,083
I return to Xizhou,

388
00:25:55,163 --> 00:25:57,323
at most, I'll be held in
Protector-General's Mansion for a few days.

389
00:25:59,123 --> 00:26:00,403
Protector-General Qu and Minister

390
00:26:01,163 --> 00:26:02,643
will not make it difficult for me.

391
00:26:04,203 --> 00:26:06,043
Why would you want to take that risk?

392
00:26:07,904 --> 00:26:08,992
Furthermore,

393
00:26:09,643 --> 00:26:10,923
if this matter were to be spread out,

394
00:26:11,883 --> 00:26:13,123
it would harm the reputation of the Tang army.

395
00:26:15,003 --> 00:26:16,523
A little mishandling by His Majesty

396
00:26:17,443 --> 00:26:18,923
could hurt people of Xizhou.

397
00:26:20,923 --> 00:26:21,923
For me alone,

398
00:26:23,403 --> 00:26:24,603
why would you do so?

399
00:26:26,272 --> 00:26:27,328
Liuli.

400
00:26:28,443 --> 00:26:29,603
Can you promise me

401
00:26:31,243 --> 00:26:33,083
not to act rashly like this in the future?

402
00:26:37,312 --> 00:26:38,464
Shouyue.

403
00:26:39,083 --> 00:26:40,883
I have never acted rashly,

404
00:26:40,883 --> 00:26:42,243
I can't promise you either.

405
00:26:43,323 --> 00:26:45,003
I am not you.

406
00:26:45,003 --> 00:26:46,563
I have no ambition.

407
00:26:47,243 --> 00:26:48,723
To me,

408
00:26:48,723 --> 00:26:49,903
reputation,

409
00:26:49,903 --> 00:26:51,483
family, country, His Majesty,

410
00:26:51,483 --> 00:26:53,403
are not as important as your safety.

411
00:26:54,363 --> 00:26:55,363
No matter what,

412
00:26:55,923 --> 00:26:57,443
I can't watch you suffer.

413
00:26:58,283 --> 00:26:59,523
If there really is a next time,

414
00:27:00,163 --> 00:27:01,443
I would definitely do it again.

415
00:27:14,592 --> 00:27:17,181
[Pei's Mansion]

416
00:27:23,883 --> 00:27:26,483
There is still no word from the camp.

417
00:27:30,003 --> 00:27:31,543
If the decree comes later,

418
00:27:31,543 --> 00:27:32,763
it doesn't matter.

419
00:27:33,363 --> 00:27:34,883
But Ni came back to say

420
00:27:34,883 --> 00:27:37,183
that Master. Mi in the warehouse
of the medicine shop

421
00:27:37,183 --> 00:27:38,483
is about to go crazy from the suppression.

422
00:27:40,363 --> 00:27:41,643
Considering his character,

423
00:27:41,643 --> 00:27:42,723
it's good for him to suppress a bit.

424
00:27:43,803 --> 00:27:45,943
But that Han Si is really amazing,

425
00:27:45,943 --> 00:27:47,683
has such kind of miraculous medicine.

426
00:27:48,843 --> 00:27:50,923
In fact, that medicine is not that miraculous.

427
00:27:50,923 --> 00:27:52,923
It was originally used by doctors,

428
00:27:52,923 --> 00:27:55,883
an antique method used for limb continuation,
bone connecting, or cutting flesh to remove decay.

429
00:27:56,563 --> 00:27:59,243
After taking it, one would fall
into a deep unconscious state,

430
00:27:59,243 --> 00:28:01,743
the breath and heartbeat become slow,

431
00:28:01,743 --> 00:28:03,483
and one would feel no pain at all.

432
00:28:04,083 --> 00:28:05,243
It looks frightening.

433
00:28:05,243 --> 00:28:06,903
But if you look closely,

434
00:28:06,903 --> 00:28:08,363
you would definitely know it.

435
00:28:09,643 --> 00:28:12,803
It's just that Han Si tampered
with Master. Mi's body and face,

436
00:28:12,803 --> 00:28:14,643
so his look scared people first,

437
00:28:15,243 --> 00:28:17,683
then he stabbed him in the palm
with a silver needle,

438
00:28:18,203 --> 00:28:20,203
other saw that Master. Mi had no reaction,

439
00:28:20,203 --> 00:28:21,643
of course would believe he's dead.

440
00:28:22,643 --> 00:28:24,483
It's nothing but a deceptive trick, after all.

441
00:28:25,043 --> 00:28:26,323
But that Master. Mi

442
00:28:26,323 --> 00:28:28,623
had been sleeping for more than two days.

443
00:28:28,623 --> 00:28:30,143
I heard from Han Si,

444
00:28:30,143 --> 00:28:31,943
he might give him too much dose.

445
00:28:31,943 --> 00:28:33,803
It turns out that the dose
for a calf and a human

446
00:28:33,803 --> 00:28:35,243
is somewhat different.

447
00:28:36,963 --> 00:28:39,723
And Sister runs a medicine shop in the city,

448
00:28:39,723 --> 00:28:41,603
there is a vacancy for a resident doctor,

449
00:28:41,603 --> 00:28:43,443
so I recommended Han Si.

450
00:28:43,443 --> 00:28:45,003
As time goes by,

451
00:28:45,003 --> 00:28:46,683
looks like they're
having a thing for each other.

452
00:29:25,923 --> 00:29:26,923
It's you.

453
00:29:28,323 --> 00:29:29,983
My lady is held up by something.

454
00:29:29,983 --> 00:29:32,603
She asks you to take the last two days
of homework and do some practice.

455
00:29:32,603 --> 00:29:34,763
She'll come to teach you
drawing when she's done.

456
00:29:35,403 --> 00:29:37,163
She has nothing to do,

457
00:29:37,723 --> 00:29:39,383
but her husband has returned,

458
00:29:39,383 --> 00:29:41,603
so she doesn't want to accompany me.

459
00:29:42,523 --> 00:29:43,723
They are all

460
00:29:43,723 --> 00:29:45,043
in pairs.

461
00:29:45,043 --> 00:29:46,443
I'm all alone,

462
00:29:46,443 --> 00:29:47,763
lonely and miserable.

463
00:29:48,723 --> 00:29:50,223
You misunderstood.

464
00:29:50,223 --> 00:29:52,283
It's Minister Qu coming
to visit the Chancellor.

465
00:29:52,283 --> 00:29:53,843
My lady is with him,

466
00:29:53,843 --> 00:29:55,163
getting held up.

467
00:29:55,163 --> 00:29:56,443
Minister is here?

468
00:29:56,443 --> 00:29:57,632
Yes.

469
00:30:00,992 --> 00:30:02,080
My lady.

470
00:30:04,003 --> 00:30:05,152
Minister.

471
00:30:08,443 --> 00:30:09,803
Why didn't you come

472
00:30:10,523 --> 00:30:11,523
to see brother-in-law that day?

473
