478
00:30:24,083 --> 00:30:25,423
Chancellor, please rest for a few days.

479
00:30:25,423 --> 00:30:26,583
No need to worry about official business.

480
00:30:26,583 --> 00:30:28,563
I have something to do and must leave now.

481
00:30:35,843 --> 00:30:36,896
I…

482
00:30:43,003 --> 00:30:44,064
Minister.

483
00:30:46,803 --> 00:30:47,923
I have something to ask you.

484
00:30:48,443 --> 00:30:49,600
What is it?

485
00:30:57,163 --> 00:30:58,176
I…

486
00:30:59,483 --> 00:31:01,303
I'll leave if you don't mind.

487
00:31:01,303 --> 00:31:03,003
I heard that you don't like women.

488
00:31:08,123 --> 00:31:09,603
Is this true?

489
00:31:13,363 --> 00:31:14,723
Who told you so?

490
00:31:14,723 --> 00:31:16,543
Zhang Minniang told me.

491
00:31:16,543 --> 00:31:19,203
She said she was worried that
I would suffer due to unrequited love.

492
00:31:20,043 --> 00:31:21,603
So I want to ask you in person.

493
00:31:22,323 --> 00:31:24,043
Although Zhang Minniang doesn't mean well,

494
00:31:25,043 --> 00:31:26,203
she did help me.

495
00:31:30,643 --> 00:31:31,712
Indeed.

496
00:31:33,203 --> 00:31:34,803
I just don't like women.

497
00:31:34,803 --> 00:31:36,483
What's so good about men?

498
00:31:36,483 --> 00:31:37,843
What's so good about women?

499
00:32:12,603 --> 00:32:13,632
Yunyi.

500
00:32:14,803 --> 00:32:15,872
Yunyi.

501
00:32:17,443 --> 00:32:19,163
You must have seen him clearly this time.

502
00:32:31,123 --> 00:32:32,603
You just went after him,

503
00:32:32,603 --> 00:32:34,283
what did you say to Minister?

504
00:32:34,283 --> 00:32:36,763
Why have you been so distracted
since you got back?

505
00:32:41,363 --> 00:32:42,496
Sister.

506
00:32:42,496 --> 00:32:43,643
Well,

507
00:32:44,523 --> 00:32:46,323
Minister is so handsome

508
00:32:46,323 --> 00:32:47,843
