509
00:32:48,723 --> 00:32:50,203
Machinery manufacturing,

510
00:32:50,203 --> 00:32:51,763
managing a business,

511
00:32:51,763 --> 00:32:53,243
governing Xizhou,

512
00:32:53,243 --> 00:32:54,523
and benefiting the people,

513
00:32:55,403 --> 00:32:56,483
