537
00:33:50,683 --> 00:33:52,043
Minister was quite scared.

538
00:33:56,603 --> 00:33:57,683
Where are you going to?

539
00:33:58,243 --> 00:33:59,563
I'm going to tell Zhang Minniang

540
00:33:59,563 --> 00:34:00,803
