543
00:34:44,043 --> 00:34:45,403
What urgent matter could she possibly have?

544
00:34:46,163 --> 00:34:48,163
Find an excuse to send her away.

545
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,240
Wait.

546
00:34:51,243 --> 00:34:54,443
If she comes again, just reject her.
Don't come to inform me.

547
00:34:55,523 --> 00:34:56,544
Yes.

548
00:35:22,123 --> 00:35:23,163
I heard

549
00:35:23,163 --> 00:35:25,743
when Minister was a hostage in Chang'an before,

550
00:35:25,743 --> 00:35:27,803
he was entangled by many noble and royal women.

551
00:35:27,803 --> 00:35:30,823
So Minister made a deliberate act of liking men

552
00:35:30,823 --> 00:35:31,883
to stay away from trouble.

553
00:36:35,043 --> 00:36:36,096
Lady Zhang.

554
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:39,168
Lady Zhang.

555
00:36:40,384 --> 00:36:41,472
Lady Zhang.

556
00:36:42,243 --> 00:36:43,663
Lady Yun, you are also here.

557
00:36:43,663 --> 00:36:44,843
We really have a fate.

558
00:36:44,843 --> 00:36:47,003
I came to your mansion to look for you
several times, but you weren't there.

559
00:36:47,563 --> 00:36:48,883
Why do you come to me?

560
00:36:48,883 --> 00:36:50,163
I wanted to tell you

561
00:36:50,163 --> 00:36:52,523
last time you told me Minister likes men,

562
00:36:52,523 --> 00:36:53,643
it was a misunderstanding.

563
00:36:54,243 --> 00:36:55,923
She said Minister likes men.

564
00:36:57,243 --> 00:36:58,803
I didn't tell you that before.

565
00:36:58,803 --> 00:37:00,683
Why are you slandering Minister and me?

566
00:37:02,592 --> 00:37:03,603
Lady Zhang.

567
00:37:04,243 --> 00:37:06,323
It's what you said last time
in the courtyard of Village Mayor Zhou.

568
00:37:06,323 --> 00:37:07,643
Did you forget it?

569
00:37:07,643 --> 00:37:08,763
I wanted to tell you

570
00:37:08,763 --> 00:37:11,043
it's not good for Minister's reputation

571
00:37:11,043 --> 00:37:12,723
to spread such rumors like this.

572
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,803
My lady.

573
00:37:14,803 --> 00:37:15,904
Lady Zhang.

574
00:37:15,904 --> 00:37:17,023
Yunyi.

575
00:37:17,023 --> 00:37:18,443
I tried to reason you properly,

576
00:37:18,443 --> 00:37:19,483
why did you push me?

577
00:37:20,443 --> 00:37:22,483
It's bleeding. You are bleeding a lot.

578
00:37:22,483 --> 00:37:24,503
What are you still doing?
Hurry and report to Minister.

579
00:37:24,503 --> 00:37:25,643
Yes, yes.

580
00:37:26,243 --> 00:37:27,243
She's bleeding.

581
00:37:45,683 --> 00:37:48,123
I really, really didn't push Zhang Minniang.

582
00:37:48,123 --> 00:37:49,403
I just wanted to tell her

583
00:37:49,403 --> 00:37:51,083
Minister does not like men.

584
00:37:52,083 --> 00:37:55,283
Lady Zhang is a noblewoman in Xizhou.

585
00:37:55,283 --> 00:37:57,363
Why would she intentionally frame you?

586
00:37:58,123 --> 00:38:00,563
Is there some kind of misunderstanding?

587
00:38:02,208 --> 00:38:03,363
You don't trust me?

588
00:38:03,363 --> 00:38:04,643
I…

589
00:38:04,643 --> 00:38:05,683
Sister, what about you?

590
00:38:05,683 --> 00:38:07,763
Do you also trust Zhang Minniang
and not trust me?

591
00:38:08,683 --> 00:38:11,683
I swear I really, really didn't push her.

592
00:38:11,683 --> 00:38:13,803
Yes, I certainly trust you.

593
00:38:17,483 --> 00:38:20,563
Were there people around
who could testify for you?

594
00:38:22,723 --> 00:38:23,963
The one who can testify

595
00:38:23,963 --> 00:38:25,683
is only Zhang Minniang's maid.

596
00:38:27,923 --> 00:38:29,023
Don't worry.

597
00:38:29,023 --> 00:38:31,283
You said Zhang Minniang
can still shout and yell

598
00:38:31,283 --> 00:38:32,543
after falling down,

599
00:38:32,543 --> 00:38:34,683
I think the fall is not serious.

600
00:38:35,323 --> 00:38:36,923
Let's bring a doctor and supplements

601
00:38:36,923 --> 00:38:38,383
to visit Zhang Minniang.

602
00:38:38,383 --> 00:38:40,223
Make a big deal small.

603
00:38:40,223 --> 00:38:42,283
What? I didn't push her at all.

604
00:38:42,283 --> 00:38:44,823
She wronged me. Why are we going to visit her?

605
00:38:44,823 --> 00:38:46,163
She's a noblewoman in Xizhou,

606
00:38:46,163 --> 00:38:47,983
also a relative of the Qu family.

607
00:38:47,983 --> 00:38:49,483
We could not just leave her.

608
00:38:50,363 --> 00:38:52,423
The necessary courtesies must be observed.

609
00:38:52,423 --> 00:38:53,443
I promise you

610
00:38:53,443 --> 00:38:54,723
I never let you be wronged.

611
00:38:54,723 --> 00:38:55,883
Do you trust me?

612
00:39:01,323 --> 00:39:02,464
I…

613
00:39:03,883 --> 00:39:06,243
Ni, go get Physician Han.

614
00:39:06,243 --> 00:39:08,243
Ask him to accompany us to Zhang's Mansion.

615
00:39:08,243 --> 00:39:09,344
Yes.

616
00:39:31,043 --> 00:39:32,443
You are not seriously injured.

617
00:39:33,843 --> 00:39:35,483
How does your maid serve her duties?

618
00:39:36,123 --> 00:39:38,083
The word got around quite a bit.

619
00:39:38,723 --> 00:39:39,983
You don't know that.

620
00:39:39,983 --> 00:39:42,323
When Yunyi pushed My lady,

621
00:39:42,323 --> 00:39:43,523
how ruthless she was.

622
00:39:44,163 --> 00:39:46,063
Thankfully, My lady has a light body,

623
00:39:46,063 --> 00:39:47,683
but she still injured her arm

624
00:39:47,683 --> 00:39:48,963
and lost so much blood.

625
00:39:48,963 --> 00:39:50,208
It hurts.

626
00:39:50,208 --> 00:39:51,328
My lady.

627
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:54,912
My lady.

628
00:39:58,323 --> 00:39:59,323
For no reason at all,

629
00:40:00,683 --> 00:40:02,003
why would Yunyi push you?

630
00:40:03,563 --> 00:40:04,883
It's not for no reason.

631
00:40:05,843 --> 00:40:07,443
T-That Yunyi

632
00:40:07,443 --> 00:40:09,323
heard some rumors

633
00:40:10,123 --> 00:40:12,003
that you like men,

634
00:40:12,003 --> 00:40:14,023
so she ran to ask My lady for verification.

635
00:40:14,023 --> 00:40:15,203
My lady

636
00:40:15,203 --> 00:40:16,763
couldn't stand someone slandering you,

637
00:40:16,763 --> 00:40:18,243
so she earnestly advised her.

638
00:40:18,243 --> 00:40:19,943
There are many worshippers
in the Great Buddha Temple,

639
00:40:19,943 --> 00:40:21,603
how could she say something like this,

640
00:40:21,603 --> 00:40:23,343
spreading the rumor about you

641
00:40:23,343 --> 00:40:24,763
and damaging your reputation?

642
00:40:25,363 --> 00:40:27,083
Yunyi refused to listen to it,

643
00:40:27,083 --> 00:40:29,243
but also argued with My lady
at the top of her voice.

644
00:40:29,883 --> 00:40:31,463
She got so angry

645
00:40:31,463 --> 00:40:32,723
because she couldn't convince My lady,

646
00:40:32,723 --> 00:40:34,403
so she pushed My lady to the ground.

647
00:40:44,683 --> 00:40:46,683
Madam, please wait a moment.

648
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:51,616
Shut up.

649
00:40:52,323 --> 00:40:54,043
Don't stir up trouble in front of Minister.

650
00:40:54,643 --> 00:40:56,263
Yunyi is the sister
of the lady of the Chancellor,

651
00:40:56,263 --> 00:40:58,263
