652
00:40:58,263 --> 00:40:59,923
Why would she hurt me on purpose?

653
00:41:00,483 --> 00:41:02,603
It's just a momentary mistake.

654
00:41:02,603 --> 00:41:03,744
I…

655
00:41:06,563 --> 00:41:07,683
That's not true.

656
00:41:08,443 --> 00:41:09,523
I did not push you at all.

657
00:41:09,523 --> 00:41:10,763
