660
00:41:18,283 --> 00:41:19,403
Pardon me.

661
00:41:23,723 --> 00:41:25,443
I've heard about what happened

662
00:41:25,443 --> 00:41:26,563
at the Great Buddha Temple today.

663
00:41:27,123 --> 00:41:28,583
So I brought a doctor here.

664
00:41:28,583 --> 00:41:30,003
No matter who is right or wrong,

665
00:41:30,003 --> 00:41:31,803
