Lady Zhang's injuries first.

666
00:41:32,643 --> 00:41:35,723
How can you not care about
who's right or wrong, Sister?

667
00:41:35,723 --> 00:41:37,403
I must speak to her face to face

668
00:41:37,403 --> 00:41:38,803
