in front of Minister.

670
00:41:41,443 --> 00:41:42,483
Be patient and stay calm.

671
00:41:43,232 --> 00:41:44,323
I trust you.

672
00:41:52,923 --> 00:41:54,283
I trust what Lady Yun said.

673
00:41:58,643 --> 00:42:01,003
